不要那么戏剧化

354
00:24:36,424 --> 00:24:38,324
Fine! Pretend there's nothing wrong!
好吧!假装一切正常

355
00:24:38,459 --> 00:24:43,624
La, di, da, di, da! lsn't it all wonderful! l'd like to know how it could get any worse!
这样不好么! 我倒想看看怎么会更糟

356
00:24:43,765 --> 00:24:45,596
- Hello, Harold. - [gasps]
- 你好，哈洛! - 什么事？

357
00:24:45,733 --> 00:24:50,693
- What happened? - Nothing, dear! Just the old hunting wound playing up a bit!
没什么 只是东征伤口有点作痛

358
00:24:51,039 --> 00:24:53,803
[chuckles] l'll just stretch it out here for a while.
伸展一下就好了

359
00:24:54,075 --> 00:24:57,010
You better get in. We need to talk.
你最好进来，我们要谈一谈

360
00:24:57,145 --> 00:24:59,636
Actually, Fairy Godmother, off to bed.
其实，神仙教母，我正要去睡觉呢

361
00:24:59,781 --> 00:25:02,909
[yawns] Already taken my pills, and they tend to make me a bit drowsy.
刚服过药，觉得有点晕晕的

362
00:25:03,051 --> 00:25:06,919
So, how about... we make this a quick visit. What?
如何呢 我们速战速决吧

363
00:25:08,189 --> 00:25:09,781
Oh, hello. Ha-ha-ha!
你好

364
00:25:12,527 --> 00:25:13,858
So, what's new?
有什么好消息？

365
00:25:13,928 --> 00:25:17,887
You remember my son, Prince Charming?
你记得我儿子白马王子吧？

366
00:25:18,032 --> 00:25:20,330
ls that you? My gosh! lt's been years.
是你啊？天哪!

367
00:25:20,435 --> 00:25:23,802
When did you get back?
好多年不见了，几时回来的？

368
00:25:24,238 --> 00:25:26,798
Oh, about five minutes ago, actually.
大约五分钟前

369
00:25:26,941 --> 00:25:30,399
After l endured blistering winds, scorching desert...
我征服了呼啸的狂风，炎热的沙漠

370
00:25:30,545 --> 00:25:33,514
l climbed to the highest room in the tallest tower...
爬上了最高塔楼里最高的房间

371
00:25:33,648 --> 00:25:35,980
Mommy can handle this.
妈妈能讲这个故事

372
00:25:36,117 --> 00:25:40,144
He endures blistering winds and scorching desert!
他征服了呼啸的狂风，炎热的沙漠

373
00:25:40,288 --> 00:25:43,883
He climbs to the highest bloody room of the tallest bloody tower...
他爬上了最高塔楼的最高房间

374
00:25:43,958 --> 00:25:45,425
And what does he find?
但是 他找到了什么？

375
00:25:45,560 --> 00:25:49,189
Some gender-confused wolf telling him that his princess
不男不女的大老狼说公主

376
00:25:49,330 --> 00:25:51,161
is already married.
请让我 已经结婚了

377
00:25:51,299 --> 00:25:53,699
lt wasn't my fault. He didn't get there in time.
不能怪我，他没有及时赶到

378
00:25:53,835 --> 00:25:55,530
Stop the car!
停车!

379
00:25:57,071 --> 00:25:58,732
Harold.
哈洛

380
00:26:00,041 --> 00:26:04,478
You force me to do something l really don't want to do.
你要强迫我做我不愿做的事

381
00:26:04,946 --> 00:26:06,413
[gasps] Where are we?
我们讲到哪里了？

382
00:26:06,547 --> 00:26:09,516
Hi. Welcome to Friar's Fat Boy! May l take your order?
你好!欢迎光临肥仔速食!请点菜

383
00:26:09,650 --> 00:26:13,017
My diet is ruined! l hope you're happy. Er... okay.
我的饮食结构 都被你毁了，你高兴了？

384
00:26:14,021 --> 00:26:16,615
Two Renaissance Wraps, no mayo... chili rings...
两个文艺复兴卷饼 辣椒卷

385
00:26:16,758 --> 00:26:20,922
