卷肉饼呢？ 你到底要什么？

388
00:26:23,631 --> 00:26:24,689

不必了，谢谢

389
00:26:24,832 --> 00:26:28,632
Your order, Fairy Godmother. This comes with the Medieval Meal.
您要的菜，神仙教母 这是中世记餐

390
00:26:28,770 --> 00:26:29,930
There you are, dear.
给你，亲爱的

391
00:26:31,339 --> 00:26:33,330

肥仔速食

392
00:26:33,408 --> 00:26:37,708
We made a deal, Harold, and l assume you don't want me to go back on my part.
我们讲好的，哈洛 你不希望我食言吧？

393
00:26:38,246 --> 00:26:39,406
[sighs deeply] lndeed not.
不要

394
00:26:39,547 --> 00:26:43,142
So, Fiona and Charming will be together.
那么费欧娜要和白马王子在一起

395
00:26:43,718 --> 00:26:45,879
