Dear Knight, I pray that you take this favor as a token of my gratitude.
亲爱的骑士 我祈祷你把这个当作我的感谢

438
00:30:52,566 --> 00:30:53,590

日记

439
00:30:56,470 --> 00:30:57,835
Dear Diary...
亲爱的日记

440
00:30:58,072 --> 00:31:00,597
Sleeping Beauty is having a slumber party tomorrow,
睡美人明天要开睡衣晚会

441
00:31:00,675 --> 00:31:04,509
but Dad says I can't go. He never lets me out after sunset.
但是爸爸不让我去 他从来不让我日落后出门

442
00:31:05,413 --> 00:31:07,438
Dad says I'm going away for a while.
爸爸说我要出去一阵子

443
00:31:07,882 --> 00:31:10,578
Must be like some finishing school.
一定是像钓鱼学校什么的

444
00:31:11,552 --> 00:31:13,452
Mom says that when I'm old enough,
妈妈说等我长大些

445
00:31:13,587 --> 00:31:18,883
my Prince Charming will rescue me from my tower and bring me back to my family,
白马王子会营救我带我回家

446
00:31:19,060 --> 00:31:22,188
and we'll all live happily ever after.
我们会从此幸福快乐的在一起

447
00:31:24,198 --> 00:31:26,029
Mrs. Fiona Charming.
白马王子太太

448
00:31:27,535 --> 00:31:28,797
Mrs. Fiona Charming.
白马王子太太

449
00:31:29,537 --> 00:31:34,440
Mrs. Fiona Charming. [echoing] Mrs. Fiona Charming.
白马王子太太

450
00:31:42,950 --> 00:31:45,783
Sorry. l hope l'm not interrupting anything.
抱歉，希望我没有打扰你

451
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:51,517
No, no. l was just reading a, uh... a scary book.
没有 我正在看恐怖小说

452
00:31:51,959 --> 00:31:56,293
l was hoping you'd let me apologize for my despicable behavior earlier.
我想为我的不恰当行为道歉

453
00:31:56,430 --> 00:31:57,419
- Okay...
好吧

454
00:31:57,631 --> 00:31:59,155
- l don't know what came over me.
我不知道自己怎么搞的

455
00:31:59,233 --> 00:32:02,669
Do you suppose we could pretend it never happened and start over...
不知能不能假装那种事没发生过

456
00:32:02,803 --> 00:32:05,704
- Look, Your Majesty, l just... - Please. Call me Dad.
- 陛下，我只是 - 请叫我爸爸

457
00:32:05,973 --> 00:32:10,069
Dad. We both acted like ogres.
爸爸，我们都缺乏文明举止

458
00:32:10,211 --> 00:32:13,612
Maybe we just need some time to get to know each other.
也许我们需要一点时间互相了解

459
00:32:13,748 --> 00:32:18,185
Excellent idea! l was actually hoping you might join me for a morning hunt.
好主意，不知你 是否愿意跟我一起去打猎

460
00:32:18,319 --> 00:32:20,287
A little father-son time?
一点父子相处的时间

461
00:32:21,989 --> 00:32:24,617
l know it would mean the world to Fiona.
费欧娜肯定会很高兴

462
00:32:33,467 --> 00:32:37,494
Shall we say, 7:30 by the old oak?
明早7：30在老橡树旁

463
00:32:43,010 --> 00:32:45,035
[Shrek] Face it, Donkey! We're lost.
承认吧，驴子，我们失败了

464
00:32:45,179 --> 00:32:47,909
We can't be lost. We followed the King's instructions exactly.
我们不能失败 我们一字不差地听从国王的指示

465
00:32:47,982 --> 00:32:48,971
What's did he say
他说什么？

466
00:32:49,049 --> 00:32:50,983
''Head to the darkest part of the woods...''
- 朝向丛林的最深，最黑暗处 - 对

467
00:32:51,051 --> 00:32:53,383
''Past the sinister trees with scary-looking branches.''
走过邪恶之树 那些长着恐怖模样的枝杈

468
00:32:53,454 --> 00:32:54,284
Check
检查

469
00:32:54,355 --> 00:32:58,849
- The bush shaped like Shirley Bassey! - We passed that three times already!
- 那些像雪丽巴瑟的树林 - 我们已经越过三次了

470
00:32:58,993 --> 00:33:01,826
You were the one who said not to stop for directions.
是你说的不要停下来

471
00:33:01,962 --> 00:33:06,126
Oh, great. My one chance to fix things up with Fiona's dad
很好，这是我唯一 与老岳父搞好关系的机会

472
00:33:06,200 --> 00:33:08,361
and l end up lost in the woods with you!
让我在树林里跟着你迷路了

473
00:33:08,502 --> 00:33:10,697
Don't get huffy! l'm only trying to help.
别那么大脾气，我不过想帮你罢了

474
00:33:10,838 --> 00:33:12,806
l know! l know.
我知道!

475
00:33:15,176 --> 00:33:18,111
- l'm sorry, all right? - Hey, don't worry about it.
- 抱歉了 - 别介意

476
00:33:18,345 --> 00:33:21,508
l just really need to make things work with this guy.
我很想跟他建立友好关系

477
00:33:21,649 --> 00:33:24,447
Yeah, sure. Now let's go bond with Daddy.
当然，我们跟老爸努力建立关系

478
00:33:32,426 --> 00:33:33,791
Well, well, well, Donkey.
驴子

479
00:33:33,928 --> 00:33:37,420
l know it was kind of a tender moment back there, but the purring?
我知道他温柔动人 不过故意发出噪音？

480
00:33:37,565 --> 00:33:39,260
What? l ain't purring.
你讲什么？我没乱吵

481
00:33:39,433 --> 00:33:42,197
Sure. What's next? A hug?
下来拥抱吗？

482
00:33:42,336 --> 00:33:45,931
Hey, Shrek. Donkeys don't purr. What do you think l am, some kind of a...
驴子不会那样，你以为我是什么呢

483
00:33:46,807 --> 00:33:48,604
Ha-ha! Fear me, if you dare!
有胆就怕我!

484
00:33:49,476 --> 00:33:50,738
[hisses] Look! A little cat.
看，一只小猫

485
00:33:50,811 --> 00:33:52,244
- Look out, Shrek! He got a piece! 
小心，史莱克!他有武器

486
00:33:52,313 --> 00:33:56,550
- lt's a cat, Donkey.Come here, little kitty, kitty.
一只小猫罢了，小猫咪

487
00:33:56,550 --> 00:34:01,647
Come on, little kitty. Come here. Oh! Come here, little kitty.
过来，小猫咪

488
00:34:04,658 --> 00:34:08,924
- Hold on, Shrek! l'm coming! - Come on! Get it off! Get it off!
- 慢着，史莱克，我来了! - 快来，下来!下来!

489
00:34:15,002 --> 00:34:17,402
- Look out, Shrek! Hold still! - Get it off!
- 小心，史莱克!别动! - 走开!

490
00:34:17,471 --> 00:34:19,462
Shrek! Hold still!
史莱克!不要动!

491
00:34:20,708 --> 00:34:24,576
- Did l miss? - No. You got them.
- 我错过了？ - 没有，你打中了

492
00:34:28,249 --> 00:34:31,844
Now, ye ogre, pray for mercy from...
你这个怪物，赶快求饶

493
00:34:33,554 --> 00:34:36,387
Puss... in Boots!
鞋猫剑客

494
00:34:36,523 --> 00:34:38,115
l'll kill that cat!
我要宰了那只猫

495
00:34:58,245 --> 00:35:01,043
- [chuckles] Hairball. - Oh! That is nasty!
- 毛球! - 真恶心

496
00:35:02,349 --> 00:35:03,782
What should we do with him?
我们拿他怎么办？

497
00:35:03,851 --> 00:35:07,480
Take the sword and neuter him. Give him the Bob Barker treatment.
我看我们拿了剑把他当场解决 像电视上那样解决他

498
00:35:07,588 --> 00:35:08,919
Oh, no! Por favor! Please!
妈妈呀!不要! 

499
00:35:08,923 --> 00:35:12,324
l implore you! lt was nothing personal, Senor.
求你!这的确是没有什么私人恩怨

500
00:35:12,393 --> 00:35:17,564
l was doing it only for my family. My mother, she is sick. And my father lives off the garbage!
我这样只是为了母亲，她生着病 我父亲靠捡垃圾过日子

501
00:35:17,564 --> 00:35:20,658
